DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260328T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260328T223000
SUMMARY:20s 30s Social Party & Activities in toronto
DESCRIPTION:20s 30s Toronto Social & Activities\nHey Toronto!\n\nThis is y
 our weekly escape into global cultures.\n\n[[[Click this WhatsApp Groupcha
 t Link to join](https://chat.whatsapp.com/Liiuvdrax8d6nywXcfXDMV) ]]\n\nEv
 ery Saturday at 7:30 PM\, people in their 20s and 30s gather for a mix of 
 language practice\, travel stories\, and community.\n\nWhether you’re ne
 w in town or born here\, this is where world citizens connect.\n\nNo judgm
 ent\, no pressure — just pure\, human interaction.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/20s-30s-toronto-social-activities/eve
 nts/312173603/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251125T234308Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251125T234308Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
